          <title>
            <string language="en">The white blood cells</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die weißen Blutzellen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les cellules de sang blanches</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">As pilhas de sangue brancas</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Le cellule di anima bianche</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τα λευκά κύτταρα αίματος</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Las células de sangre blancas</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This diagram shows the two possible actions that white blood cells do to destroy bacteria.  One is enclosing and destroying the bacteria (top) and another is creating antibodies that will destroy the bacteria (bottom).</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">antibodies</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">bacteria</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">defence</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">white blood cells</string>
          </keyword>
          <structure>
            <source>structureValues</source>
            <value>atomic</value>
          </structure>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Diagramm zeigt den zwei möglichen 
Tätigkeiten, daß weiße Blutzellen tun, um Bakterium zu zerstören. 
Eins ist umgebend und das Zerstören des Bakteriums (Oberseite) 
und der ander stellt Antikörper her, die das Bakterium (Unterseite) 
zerstören.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Ce diagramme prouve aux deux actions possibles que
les cellules de sang blanches font pour détruire des bactéries. 
On est entourant et détruire les bactéries (dessus) et des 
autres crée les anticorps qui détruiront les bactéries (bas).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Este diagrama mostra às duas ações possíveis 
que as pilhas de sangue brancas fazem para destruir as bactérias. 
Um é incluindo e destruir as bactérias (alto) e outras está 
criando os antibodies que destruirão as bactérias (fundo).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questo schema indica alle due azioni possibili 
che le cellule di anima bianche fanno per distruggere i batteri. 
Uno è accludente e distruggere i batteri (parte superiore)
ed un altro sta creando gli anticorpi che distruggeranno i batteri 
(parte inferiore).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό το διάγραμμα εμφανίζει δύο πιθανές ενέργειες 
ότι τα λευκά κύτταρα αίματος κάνουν για να καταστρέψουν τα 
βακτηρίδια. Κάποιος εσωκλείει και καταστρέφει τα βακτηρίδια
(κορυφή) και άλλος δημιουργεί τα αντισώματα που θα καταστρέψουν 
τα βακτηρίδια (κατώτατο σημείο).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Este diagrama muestra a dos acciones posibles que 
las células de sangre blancas hacen para destruir bacterias. 
Uno es que incluye y destruir las bacterias (tapa) y otras está
creando los anticuerpos que destruirán las bacterias (fondo).</string>
          </description>
